Snowfall can start suddenly
A truly cool winter is what Wolfgang Brauburger wants.
It is not at all something with which you want to make life impossible for citizens, says the director of road maintenance in winter of the FES
But with this, your employees can learn to test and master all vehicular technology.
Meteorologists may announce it for the first time over the weekend.
More than 330 employees and 120 vehicles are ready to deal with snow and ice.
In this case, the ESF acts in accordance with a detailed plan.
